des:
Liz Rau is definitely an oddball with quirky humor and varied interests. She's an author, wine lover, cat lady, vegetarian, wanderlust traveler, Missouri raised and a Colorado implant. Some would call her a dreamer, others would say she's obsessed with pop culture and reality TV. 

But recently, she's undergone a major change in her life: VSG Bariatric surgery. Yep, "Liz got Sleeved". Now she's on a journey to discover health, happiness and true acceptance of the body she was born with. Join her as she navigates all of this with a brand new view on life.

Follow on Instagram, Facebook & Twitter (@LizRauOfficial). 
#LizGotSleeved 

www.LizRauOfficial.com > Blog and Shop.
